{
  "id": "RAW_bcf48717",
  "title": "Sora 关停背后：为啥它没跑成“视频版 ChatGPT”？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDE0Mjc4MA==&mid=2651279895&idx=4&sn=22366f045354917507d6596d1546d94d",
  "date": "2026-03-26 05:48:00",
  "author": "InfoQ 中文",
  "siteName": "InfoQ 中文",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span>InfoQ</span> <span>2026-03-26 13:48</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">浙江</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3cd87618&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FhLLZnAbUwNgFiaJoPSjibRlwNP5gBmuyIuqiaqq7vlT69RFFR44nPb1XEKU9RwHdGZO56v6tBkbat1jFDjrRdQqZYG4TcrXhSQ0ibjhk771vAvA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>当OpenAI开始讲ROI，高成本低频需求先出局</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15625\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"90\" data-imgfileid=\"503629017\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=778e4015&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FYriaiaJPb26VPQqHC66RJFpttVIMWG83T3lWHahUD4bvhxlKSayjeV2ibvC5ydqklP9QHDPD3qHJM07TV3IfHstjA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></p>\n  <div style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;margin: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;text-align: center;margin: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">一代爆火的视频生成 AI，居然在凌晨“猝死”了：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI Sora 宣布关停，彻底关停。</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">消息一出，很快就在社交媒体上刷屏了，目前 Sora 的这篇帖子已经有超 1100 万浏览。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7157407407407408\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"503796227\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=21837769&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNiaicrlnGsBO1Jld5mVYUhdPGX22SumdaLpQkPadOGduYMAfld3EjfIX8MMOcryBqDnU4qJWOFcbRKO111FTscics9tMgQlNn4iaeo%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">不过细看 Sora 原帖的评论区，评价两极分化明显。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">一方面，有用户惋惜其生成效果的真实感，认为在当前阶段，这样的表现依然难得。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9203703703703704\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"503796228\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d658f112&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNjjetia17vreOsiaeibS8IiaetB7mZSvrR1aqT3l1ecBFz0y1hfbeHlOdY2TYHY0hGEJe61KMG07LibzI4LTv0wkIxWa9CspNmhZ71A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">还有人表示，Sora 是一个“虽不完美但仍有价值”的创作工具。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4722222222222222\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"503796225\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0636e40f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNhLpEsNnxv1Lia0tic2hUkkpxiawu6cyTI3j41Uwwxicib3TQlRDVFIA11sMkUpKo5Xkv4YGwacypcVd0eXUQygJLDqaricmsicrwDHNM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">另一方面，质疑和嘲讽声音在评论区其实稍占上风。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如，有网友直指其长期存在的版权与内容风险，认为平台充斥侵权与虚假信息：“我很高兴看到 Sora 被关闭，你们对人类根本毫无益处”。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3148148148148148\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"503796226\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=953f8924&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNg7DLmnWkZsgqibdDmdlcrdMVK45VoGpGSYdb6fB6WQZyC9BScVia35aGBoicvNib44w58n3flZddcu7TkyDIu41nTwHEbChchMru8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">有人拿着 Grok 做的动图拱火道，这恐怕要让唱衰 OpenAI 的马斯克乐坏了。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0537037037037038\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"503796229\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=882a728e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNiaics2ywk2sj4wiaX6HV5bwF3ROUSl4kqYqib94iaMuEAgjlfxt38b0Lo2iaIUdJZkdFwWvXPKyEHDxvCMLSQSRaEMqicichrBkcRpMds%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">还有网友表示，Sora 没了？不慌，我们还有 Seedance 2.0、可灵等一堆更好用的视频生成工具。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.40370370370370373\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"503796232\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4d131007&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNia1zuhz2U6yICXPyRJRg16lqibXJqMzg5bL0iaxI7kua4kcxTibibqdjJRNaicgFMO9lUjlPicvgMTB2qEyuou3xF3hianY9GAEkibeL7k%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">另外，就在三个月前，OpenAI 刚获得了迪士尼承诺的 10 亿美元投资，并计划引入后者的 200 多个 IP，用于 Sora 视频生成。但该合作仍停留在意向阶段，资金还未实际到账。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">而随着 Sora 项目被关停，这一合作失去了应用场景与基础，相关投资与授权计划也随之终止。</span></p>\n    <p data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;color: #00b38b;text-align: left;line-height: 35px;margin: 40px 8px 0 8px;background: none no-repeat left 28px;background-size: 100% 6px;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=704ed059&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FhLLZnAbUwNh8PAThNDqDTMDHBqqXh3kRYxAumPaB1RpzKCd0LhJThZ5ccCF4mLQBhU8N1hkJzmiaCeGib51yl4CjmNkSsd8Tuia2gBwBsS9UMQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 32px;margin-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 22px;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;Sora 为何没跑成“视频版 ChatGPT”？ </span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">Sora 刚出来时曾登顶苹果应用商店，它为什么最终没像 ChatGPT 一样成功？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">这恐怕不能简单归因于 Sora“技术不够强”，毕竟就连不少批评它的人，也承认其生成效果确实逼真。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">在笔者看来，Sora 的问题，主要在于它踩中了生成式 AI 最难的三件事：使用频率、成本结构，以及产品形态。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">2024 年，Sora 公开亮相，然后迅速以“技术奇观”的姿态出圈：生成的视频效果，一度被认为接近好莱坞影视级制作。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">2025 年 9 月，萨姆·奥特曼高调宣布 Sora 成为独立应用。它一开始其实是奔着**“AI 版 TikTok”** 去的：熟悉的竖屏刷视频，往下滑就完事。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了放大“可玩性”，Sora 还推出过一个颇具争议的功能：“cameos”。用户只要扫一下脸，就能生成一个“数字分身”，效果真实到有点离谱。而且这个分身还能设成公开——也就是说，别人也可以拿你的脸去拍视频。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如这个看着逼真而诡异视频，就是通过扫脸后，拿 Sora 做的。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.777027027027027\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"296\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"503796235\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=357d0637&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FhLLZnAbUwNiaooymVJVER6a01OQxDT11I6TMko851nmuNiaQcKa8W68p83ic5RicjYWwPWL7XvLaPWbulUjyBVUtAToRu7Xic0lRRJO5XsqVqZKs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">不过这个功能还没火多久，就惹上了官司。因为“Cameo”和一家公司重名了，对方直接把 OpenAI 告上法庭并打赢了官司，然后 Sora 只好老实把功能改名为“characters”。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">话说回来，Sora 的热度并没有转化为使用频率。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">ChatGPT 解决的是写代码、查资料、写邮件这些“每天都会发生”的需求，是典型的高频工具；而视频生成更像创作行为——大多数人不会天天做视频，更多是“偶尔用一下”。一旦使用频率上不去，留存和付费就很难成立。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">Sora 在上线初期表现极为亮眼：5 天内下载量突破 100 万，并迅速登顶 App Store 榜首 。但热度并未持续，仅一个月后，其下载量就开始明显下滑，2026 年 1 月环比下降 45%。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">再看成本。文本生成计算规模相对有限，而视频生成则更接近“算力黑洞”：分辨率、时长、帧数叠加，推理成本几乎是指数级上升。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">简单说，每生成一个视频都在持续、大量烧钱。但问题在于，用户对视频生成的付费意愿并没有同步提升，这直接导致单位经济模型难以闭环。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">有开发者测算了一下，结果显示，生成一分钟 AI 视频的计算量，保守估计，是生成一段千字文本的 10 倍以上。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.739010989010989\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"728\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"503796233\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=71a008d1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNhefXlxiazC3KMpWSibaicpXENjITo5VGGrxQaAibsfL9XfZ9XfdcpKlzQ5BDqlCVR6ORh9TIDd7zhibxo8TU2cUoO4mHo00zTCz8jk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 视频生成通常按“秒”计费，单秒成本在 0.05 到 0.75 美元之间，一个 10 秒视频成本可达 0.5 至 7.5 美元；而在一些分析中，类似 Sora 这样的视频生成工具，单个 10 秒视频的成本大约就要 1 美元。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">更关键的是产品形态。Sora 一开始被设计成“AI 版短视频平台”，形态接近 TikTok：刷内容、做 remix、分享。但 AI 生成内容天然面临同质化和“看一眼就走”的问题，很难像真人创作那样形成稳定社区。换句话说，AI 能生成内容，不等于用户愿意长期消费这些内容。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，还有一层隐性但重要的约束：版权与合规。视频相比文本更接近“作品”，一旦涉及人物、IP 和风格复现，法律风险远高于文本生成。这使得产品越强，反而越难大规模放开。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">简而言之，不是视频生成不重要，但当生成能力已经足够强时，一个能被高频使用、能自我造血的产品形态或许更能决定成败。</span></p>\n    <p data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;color: #00b38b;text-align: left;line-height: 35px;margin: 40px 8px 0 8px;background: none no-repeat left 28px;background-size: 100% 6px;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2c88e987&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FhLLZnAbUwNgo3WXneBSXmZQiciaZzhic0eC6EqaXmG2d0osfCNcFB0gRjsSwniag9YgnAyPKibzxNRz8ic29iaNNr2tcxIgkiaSY2rp6leCeWJATdG8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 32px;margin-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 22px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;IPO 临近，OpenAI 开始做减法 </span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">至于 Sora 为何在此时被关停，目前 OpenAI 并未公开说明具体原因。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">但据纽约时报消息，这一决定很可能与 OpenAI 正在筹备的 IPO（最早于今年启动）有关。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">目前，OpenAI 估值约为 7300 亿美元，正与 Anthropic 激烈争夺企业客户和投资者关注，并对业务进行聚焦和收缩。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">公开信息显示，OpenAI 去年营收约为 130 亿美元，但未来四年预计还将投入约 1000 亿美元用于基础设施建设，其中很大一部分将流向数据中心。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">在这样的资金压力下，公司必须优先保证那些能够带来持续收入与高频使用的核心产品，而不是继续为高成本、低频使用的实验性产品“输血”。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">有网友提问：现在只是停用了 Sora 应用本身，还是整个模型都停用？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5157407407407407\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"503796231\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aa9b2ef3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNgBkkia6BkB2ADmlLtmvIqALW4MP4j6qWw9neIXcnEahsWibkV3WZDLtkAOnJPQawkVqUvuaaTnSrFU7JTv6kQ63u8DEjmnPpwFw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">从目前披露的信息来看，OpenAI 关闭的是面向用户的 Sora 应用与相关服务，但视频生成技术并未消失。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">奥特曼在内部备忘录中也给出了方向：Sora 研究团队将“优先推进长期世界模拟研究，尤其是与机器人技术相关的方向”。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">事实上，调整并不只发生在 Sora 上。OpenAI 旗下的 ChatGPT、Codex 以及 Atlas 浏览器，也在面临调整、整合。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">曾经的 OpenAI，在不少员工眼中，像在同时孵化多家初创公司。但随着算力资源趋紧、产品入口分散、团队协同成本上升，这种多点开花的模式开始显现出效率问题。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">3 月 20 日，据《华尔街日报》消息，OpenAI 正计划将 ChatGPT、Codex 以及 Atlas 浏览器整合为一款桌面级 “超级应用”，把原本分散的产品入口重新收拢。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI 不再满足于做一个单纯的聊天框，而是希望打造能在电脑上自动执行任务的 AI 工作台。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">从这个角度看，Sora 的关停更像是一个信号：OpenAI 不再试图用多个“明星产品”去占位，而是回到一个更直接的问题：哪一个入口，能够承载未来最核心的使用场景。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;\">参考链接：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://x.com/soraofficialapp/status/2036546752535470382\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/soraofficialapp/status/2036546752535470382</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/mostafa-asghari-753894237_and-even-more-again-nice-lets-crunch-activity-7379137196689100800-ehnv/?utm_source\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.linkedin.com/posts/mostafa-asghari-753894237_and-even-more-again-nice-lets-crunch-activity-7379137196689100800-ehnv/?utm_source</a></span></span></p>\n   <div style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;margin: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"6 2 []\">\n    <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 16px;font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-s